# Lotto Analysis Project Rules

- Tech Stack: Next.js (App Router), TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, tRPC, Zod, TanStack Query.
- Code Quality: Use Biome for linting and formatting. Do not use Prettier/ESLint.
- Component Pattern: Use Lucide-react for icons. Create reusable UI components in @/components/ui.
- Data Validation: Always use Zod for schema validation (both frontend and backend).
- API Pattern: Use tRPC for all server communication.
- Styling: Use Tailwind CSS with a mobile-first responsive design.
- Naming: Use kebab-case for file names and PascalCase for React components.
